title: Gay- [MEN] Fuckemon Go
description:
Ash and Brock go out Pokemon hunting so that Ash can continue his quest to be a Pokemon Master. Along the way, they catch several badly named pokemon (My favorite is ButtPlugasaur). Eventually, they spot a huge Pikachu costume standing next to a rock. Naturally, Ash must catch said Pikachu. For some ungodly reason, when the ball hits Pikachu, and out pops Adam Bryant wearing a yellow speedo. That's it. like not even ears or some goddamn body paint to make it seem somewhat convincing. Just Adam Bryant in a yellow fucking speedo. Like with Men's budget, you'd think they could spring for like some cheap Pikachu ear headband or something. Like I could run down to Spencer's right now an get some for like $8. Sorry, that's the rum talking. ANYWAYS, so of course, the first thing Ash and Brock thing of is "Hey that Pikachu turned into a dude! WE HAVE to have sex with it!" Cuz, ya know, porn logic, right?
Of course Pickachu is all for it and gestures them to come over. First Brock gets fucked telling ASh "This is how you become a real trainer!" Then it's Ash's turn to ride Pikachu. I mean after this, it's fairly standard porn. Like you've watched porn before it's no different. Although I'm happy that this is a MEN porn parody where the character actually kept on a costume reminding you what the situation is (I'm looking right at you X-Men and Captain America. The straights figured it out, so can you)
